{"html":"<br/>\n<h2>Fact Symbols with Injective Instances</h2><br/>\n<p class=\"monospace rules\">None</p><br/>\n<h2>Multiset Rewriting Rules</h2><br/>\n<p class=\"monospace rules\"><span class=\"hl_keyword\">rule</span> (<span class=\"hl_keyword\">modulo</span> AC) isend:<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">[</span> !KU( x ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">]</span> <span class=\"hl_operator\">--[</span> K( x ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">]-&gt;</span> <span class=\"hl_operator\">[</span> In( x ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">]</span><br/>\n<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_comment\">/* has exactly the trivial AC variant */</span><br/>\n<br/>\n<br/>\n<span class=\"hl_keyword\">rule</span> (<span class=\"hl_keyword\">modulo</span> AC) irecv:<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">[</span> Out( x ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">]</span> <span class=\"hl_operator\">--&gt;</span> <span class=\"hl_operator\">[</span> !KD( x ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">]</span><br/>\n<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_comment\">/* has exactly the trivial AC variant */</span><br/>\n<br/>\n<br/>\n<span class=\"hl_keyword\">rule</span> (<span class=\"hl_keyword\">modulo</span> E) ChanOut_S:<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">[</span> Out_S( $A, $B, x ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">]</span><br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">--[</span> ChanOut_S( $A, $B, x ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">]-&gt;</span><br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">[</span> !Sec( $A, $B, x ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">]</span><br/>\n<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_comment\">/* has exactly the trivial AC variant */</span><br/>\n<span class=\"hl_keyword\">rule</span> (<span class=\"hl_keyword\">modulo</span> E) ChanIn_S:<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">[</span> !Sec( $A, $B, x ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">]</span><br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">--[</span> ChanIn_S( $A, $B, x ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">]-&gt;</span><br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">[</span> In_S( $A, $B, x ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">]</span><br/>\n<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_comment\">/* has exactly the trivial AC variant */</span><br/>\n<span class=\"hl_keyword\">rule</span> (<span class=\"hl_keyword\">modulo</span> E) ChanOut_A:<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">[</span> Out_A( $A, x ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">]</span><br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">--[</span> ChanOut_A( $A, x ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">]-&gt;</span><br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">[</span> !Auth( $A, x ), Out( &lt;$A, x&gt; ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">]</span><br/>\n<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_comment\">/* has exactly the trivial AC variant */</span><br/>\n<span class=\"hl_keyword\">rule</span> (<span class=\"hl_keyword\">modulo</span> E) ChanIn_A:<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">[</span> !Auth( $A, x ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">]</span> <span class=\"hl_operator\">--[</span> ChanIn_A( $A, x ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">]-&gt;</span> <span class=\"hl_operator\">[</span> In_A( $A, x ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">]</span><br/>\n<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_comment\">/* has exactly the trivial AC variant */</span><br/>\n<span class=\"hl_keyword\">rule</span> (<span class=\"hl_keyword\">modulo</span> E) ChanOut_IR_HP:<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">[</span> Out_IR_HP( $A, $B, m ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">]</span><br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">--[</span> ChanOut_IR_HP( $A, $B, m ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">]-&gt;</span><br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">[</span> Out( &lt;$A, $B, m&gt; ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">]</span><br/>\n<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_comment\">/* has exactly the trivial AC variant */</span><br/>\n<span class=\"hl_keyword\">rule</span> (<span class=\"hl_keyword\">modulo</span> E) ChanIn_IR_HP:<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">[</span> In( &lt;$A, $B, m&gt; ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">]</span><br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">--[</span> ChanIn_IR_HP( $A, $B, m ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">]-&gt;</span><br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">[</span> In_IR_HP( $A, $B, m ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">]</span><br/>\n<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_comment\">/* has exactly the trivial AC variant */</span><br/>\n<span class=\"hl_keyword\">rule</span> (<span class=\"hl_keyword\">modulo</span> E) ChanOut_IR_PS:<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">[</span> Out_IR_PS( $A, $B, m ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">]</span><br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">--[</span> ChanOut_IR_PS( $A, $B, m ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">]-&gt;</span><br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">[</span> Out( &lt;$A, $B, m&gt; ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">]</span><br/>\n<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_comment\">/* has exactly the trivial AC variant */</span><br/>\n<span class=\"hl_keyword\">rule</span> (<span class=\"hl_keyword\">modulo</span> E) ChanIn_IR_PS:<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">[</span> In( &lt;$A, $B, m&gt; ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">]</span><br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">--[</span> ChanIn_IR_PS( $A, $B, m ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">]-&gt;</span><br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">[</span> In_IR_PS( $A, $B, m ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">]</span><br/>\n<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_comment\">/* has exactly the trivial AC variant */</span><br/>\n<span class=\"hl_keyword\">rule</span> (<span class=\"hl_keyword\">modulo</span> E) ChanOut_IR_SP:<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">[</span> Out_IR_SP( $A, $B, m ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">]</span><br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">--[</span> ChanOut_IR_SP( $A, $B, m ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">]-&gt;</span><br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">[</span> Out( &lt;$A, $B, m&gt; ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">]</span><br/>\n<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_comment\">/* has exactly the trivial AC variant */</span><br/>\n<span class=\"hl_keyword\">rule</span> (<span class=\"hl_keyword\">modulo</span> E) ChanIn_IR_SP:<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">[</span> In( &lt;$A, $B, m&gt; ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">]</span><br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">--[</span> ChanIn_IR_SP( $A, $B, m ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">]-&gt;</span><br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">[</span> In_IR_SP( $A, $B, m ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">]</span><br/>\n<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_comment\">/* has exactly the trivial AC variant */</span><br/>\n<span class=\"hl_keyword\">rule</span> (<span class=\"hl_keyword\">modulo</span> E) ChanOut_IR_PH:<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">[</span> Out_IR_PH( $A, $B, m ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">]</span><br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">--[</span> ChanOut_IR_PH( $A, $B, m ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">]-&gt;</span><br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">[</span> Out( &lt;$A, $B, m&gt; ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">]</span><br/>\n<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_comment\">/* has exactly the trivial AC variant */</span><br/>\n<span class=\"hl_keyword\">rule</span> (<span class=\"hl_keyword\">modulo</span> E) ChanIn_IR_PH:<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">[</span> In( &lt;$A, $B, m&gt; ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">]</span><br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">--[</span> ChanIn_IR_PH( $A, $B, m ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">]-&gt;</span><br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">[</span> In_IR_PH( $A, $B, m ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">]</span><br/>\n<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_comment\">/* has exactly the trivial AC variant */</span><br/>\n<span class=\"hl_keyword\">rule</span> (<span class=\"hl_keyword\">modulo</span> E) fakeEvidence:<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">[</span> In( &lt;ballot, evidence&gt; ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">]</span><br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">--[</span> Evidence( ballot, evidence ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">]-&gt;</span><br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">[</span> <span class=\"hl_operator\">]</span><br/>\n<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_comment\">/* has exactly the trivial AC variant */</span><br/>\n<span class=\"hl_keyword\">rule</span> (<span class=\"hl_keyword\">modulo</span> E) publickeyinfrastructure:<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">[</span> Fr( ~skX ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">]</span><br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">--[</span> LongtermKey( $X, ~skX ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">]-&gt;</span><br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">[</span> !Ltk( $X, ~skX ), !Pk( $X, pk(~skX) ), Out( pk(~skX) ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">]</span><br/>\n<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_comment\">/* has exactly the trivial AC variant */</span><br/>\n<span class=\"hl_keyword\">rule</span> (<span class=\"hl_keyword\">modulo</span> E) Setup:<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">[</span> !Ltk( &#39;S&#39;, ~skS ), !Ltk( &#39;D1&#39;, ~sskD1 ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">]</span><br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">--[</span><br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;Setup( ),<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;BB_pskDs( &#39;BB&#39;, &lt;&#39;spkD&#39;, pk(~sskD1)&gt; ),<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;BB_pkS( &#39;BB&#39;, &lt;&#39;spkS&#39;, pk(~skS)&gt; ),<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;BB_H( &#39;BB&#39;, &lt;&#39;H&#39;, &#39;H1&#39;&gt; ),<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;CastByCorresp( &#39;H1&#39;, pk(~sskD1) ), Voter( &#39;H1&#39; ),<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;SecretKeyD( ~sskD1 ), Server( &#39;S&#39; ), Honest( &#39;S&#39; )<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">]-&gt;</span><br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">[</span><br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Out( &lt;&#39;H1&#39;, &#39;D1&#39;, &#39;P&#39;, &#39;BB&#39;, $v1<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&gt;<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;),<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;AgSt_D0( &#39;D1&#39;,<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;&#39;H1&#39;, &#39;S&#39;, pk(~skS), ~sskD1&gt;<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;),<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;AgSt_A0( &#39;A&#39;, &lt;&#39;S&#39;, &#39;BB&#39;, pk(~skS)&gt;<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;),<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;AgSt_P0( &#39;P&#39;, &#39;S&#39; ),<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;AgSt_P1( &#39;P&#39;, &#39;H1&#39; ),<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;AgSt_BB0( &#39;BB&#39;,<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;&#39;S&#39;, pk(~sskD1), pk(~skS), &#39;H1&#39;&gt;<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;),<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Out_A( &#39;BB&#39;, &lt;&#39;spkD&#39;, pk(~sskD1)&gt; ),<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Out_A( &#39;BB&#39;, &lt;&#39;spkS&#39;, pk(~skS)&gt; ),<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Out_A( &#39;BB&#39;, &lt;&#39;H&#39;, &#39;H1&#39;&gt; ),<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;AgSt_S0( &#39;S&#39;, &lt;~skS, pk(~sskD1)&gt; )<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">]</span><br/>\n<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_comment\">/* has exactly the trivial AC variant */</span><br/>\n<span class=\"hl_keyword\">rule</span> (<span class=\"hl_keyword\">modulo</span> E) D_1:<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">[</span><br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;AgSt_D0( $D, &lt;$H, $S, pkS, ~sskD&gt; ), In( &lt;$H, $D, v&gt; ),<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Fr( ~r )<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">]</span><br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">--[</span> D1( ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">]-&gt;</span><br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">[</span> Out( &lt;$D, $H, sg(encp(v, ~r, pkS), ~sskD)&gt; ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">]</span><br/>\n<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_comment\">/* has exactly the trivial AC variant */</span><br/>\n<span class=\"hl_keyword\">rule</span> (<span class=\"hl_keyword\">modulo</span> E) P:<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">[</span> AgSt_P0( $P, $S ), In_IR_HP( $H, $P, b ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">]</span><br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">--[</span> Receive_R_HP( $H, $P, b ), Send_R_PS( $P, $S, b ), P1( ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">]-&gt;</span><br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">[</span> Out_IR_PS( $P, $S, b ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">]</span><br/>\n<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_comment\">/* has exactly the trivial AC variant */</span><br/>\n<span class=\"hl_keyword\">rule</span> (<span class=\"hl_keyword\">modulo</span> E) S_1a:<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">[</span><br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;AgSt_S0( $S, &lt;~skS, pk(~sskDa)&gt; ),<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;In_IR_PS( $P, $S, sg(encp(va, ra, pk(~skS)), ~sskDa) )<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">]</span><br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">--[</span><br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;Learn_S_ballot( $S, sg(encp(va, ra, pk(~skS)), ~sskDa) ),<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;Receive_R_PS( $P, $S, sg(encp(va, ra, pk(~skS)), ~sskDa) ),<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;Send_R_SP( $S, $P, sg(sg(encp(va, ra, pk(~skS)), ~sskDa), ~skS) ),<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;S1( )<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">]-&gt;</span><br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">[</span><br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;AgSt_S1a( $S, &lt;~skS, sg(encp(va, ra, pk(~skS)), ~sskDa)&gt; ),<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Out_IR_SP( $S, $P, sg(sg(encp(va, ra, pk(~skS)), ~sskDa), ~skS) ),<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Out_A( $S, &lt;&#39;b&#39;, sg(encp(va, ra, pk(~skS)), ~sskDa)&gt;<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;),<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Out_A( $S, &lt;&#39;bPrime&#39;, encp(va, ra, pk(~skS))&gt; ),<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Out_A( $S, &lt;&#39;v&#39;, va&gt; ),<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Out_A( $S,<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;&#39;zkp&#39;, zkp(encp(va, ra, pk(~skS)), va, ~skS)&gt;<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;)<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">]</span><br/>\n<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_comment\">/* has exactly the trivial AC variant */</span><br/>\n<span class=\"hl_keyword\">rule</span> (<span class=\"hl_keyword\">modulo</span> E) P_2:<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">[</span> AgSt_P1( $P, $H ), In_IR_SP( $S, $P, c ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">]</span><br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">--[</span> Receive_R_SP( $S, $P, c ), Send_R_PH( $P, $H, c ), P2( ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">]-&gt;</span><br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">[</span> Out_IR_PH( $P, $H, c ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">]</span><br/>\n<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_comment\">/* has exactly the trivial AC variant */</span><br/>\n<span class=\"hl_keyword\">rule</span> (<span class=\"hl_keyword\">modulo</span> E) BB:<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">[</span><br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;AgSt_BB0( $BB, &lt;$S, spkDa, pkS, Ha&gt; ),<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;In_A( $S, &lt;&#39;b&#39;, ba&gt; ),<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;In_A( $S, &lt;&#39;bPrime&#39;, bPrimea&gt; ),<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;In_A( $S, &lt;&#39;v&#39;, va&gt; ),<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;In_A( $S, &lt;&#39;zkp&#39;, p&gt; )<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">]</span><br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">--[</span><br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;BB_rec( $BB, &lt;&#39;b&#39;, ba&gt; ),<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;BB_woS( $BB, &lt;&#39;bPrime&#39;, bPrimea&gt; ),<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;BB_tal( $BB, &lt;&#39;v&#39;, va&gt; ),<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;BB_zkp( $BB, &lt;&#39;zkp&#39;, p&gt; ), End( )<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">]-&gt;</span><br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">[</span><br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Out_A( $BB, &lt;&#39;b&#39;, ba&gt; ),<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Out_A( $BB, &lt;&#39;bPrime&#39;, bPrimea&gt; ),<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Out_A( $BB, &lt;&#39;v&#39;, va&gt; ),<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Out_A( $BB, &lt;&#39;zkp&#39;, p&gt; )<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">]</span><br/>\n<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_comment\">// loop breakers: [1,2,3,4]</span><br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_comment\">/* has exactly the trivial AC variant */</span><br/>\n<span class=\"hl_keyword\">rule</span> (<span class=\"hl_keyword\">modulo</span> E) A_1:<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">[</span><br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;AgSt_A0( $A, &lt;$S, $BB, pkS&gt; ),<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;In_A( $BB, &lt;&#39;b&#39;, sg(bPrimea, sskDa)&gt; ),<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;In_A( $BB, &lt;&#39;bPrime&#39;, bPrimea&gt; ),<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;In_A( $BB, &lt;&#39;v&#39;, va&gt; ),<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;In_A( $BB, &lt;&#39;zkp&#39;, p&gt; ),<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;In_A( $BB, &lt;&#39;spkD&#39;, pk(sskDa)&gt; )<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">]</span><br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">--[</span><br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;Learn_A_proof( $A, &lt;&#39;zkp&#39;, p&gt; ),<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;Learn_A_spkDSG( $A, &lt;&#39;spkD&#39;, pk(sskDa)&gt; ),<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;Learn_A_Vs( $A, &lt;&#39;v&#39;, va&gt; ),<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;Learn_A_Bs( $A, &lt;&#39;b&#39;, sg(bPrimea, sskDa)&gt; ),<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;Learn_A_bPrimes( $A, &lt;&#39;bPrime&#39;, bPrimea&gt; ),<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;VerifyA2( $A, verzkp(p, bPrimea, va, pkS) ), A1( )<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">]-&gt;</span><br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">[</span> <span class=\"hl_operator\">]</span><br/>\n<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_comment\">/* has exactly the trivial AC variant */</span></p><br/>\n<h2>Restrictions of the Set of Traces</h2><br/>\n<p class=\"monospace rules\"><span class=\"hl_keyword\">restriction</span> Chan_R_PS:<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&quot;<span class=\"hl_operator\">∀ </span>A B m #i<span class=\"hl_operator\">.</span><br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">(</span>Send_R_PS( A, B, m ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">@</span> #i<span class=\"hl_operator\">)</span> <span class=\"hl_operator\">⇒</span><br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">(</span><span class=\"hl_operator\">∃ </span>#j<span class=\"hl_operator\">.</span> Receive_R_PS( A, B, m ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">@</span> #j<span class=\"hl_operator\">)</span>&quot;<br/>\n<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_comment\">/*<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;expanded formula:<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&quot;<span class=\"hl_operator\">∀ </span>A B m #i<span class=\"hl_operator\">.</span><br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">(</span>Send_R_PS( A, B, m ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">@</span> #i<span class=\"hl_operator\">)</span> <span class=\"hl_operator\">⇒</span><br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">(</span><span class=\"hl_operator\">∃ </span>#j<span class=\"hl_operator\">.</span> Receive_R_PS( A, B, m ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">@</span> #j<span class=\"hl_operator\">)</span>&quot;<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;*/</span><br/>\n<br/>\n<span class=\"hl_keyword\">restriction</span> Chan_R_SP:<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&quot;<span class=\"hl_operator\">∀ </span>A B m #i<span class=\"hl_operator\">.</span><br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">(</span>Send_R_SP( A, B, m ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">@</span> #i<span class=\"hl_operator\">)</span> <span class=\"hl_operator\">⇒</span><br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">(</span><span class=\"hl_operator\">∃ </span>#j<span class=\"hl_operator\">.</span> Receive_R_SP( A, B, m ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">@</span> #j<span class=\"hl_operator\">)</span>&quot;<br/>\n<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_comment\">/*<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;expanded formula:<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&quot;<span class=\"hl_operator\">∀ </span>A B m #i<span class=\"hl_operator\">.</span><br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">(</span>Send_R_SP( A, B, m ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">@</span> #i<span class=\"hl_operator\">)</span> <span class=\"hl_operator\">⇒</span><br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">(</span><span class=\"hl_operator\">∃ </span>#j<span class=\"hl_operator\">.</span> Receive_R_SP( A, B, m ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">@</span> #j<span class=\"hl_operator\">)</span>&quot;<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;*/</span><br/>\n<br/>\n<span class=\"hl_keyword\">restriction</span> OneSetup:<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&quot;<span class=\"hl_operator\">∀ </span>#i #j<span class=\"hl_operator\">.</span><br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">(</span><span class=\"hl_operator\">(</span>Setup( ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">@</span> #i<span class=\"hl_operator\">)</span> <span class=\"hl_operator\">∧</span> <span class=\"hl_operator\">(</span>Setup( ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">@</span> #j<span class=\"hl_operator\">)</span><span class=\"hl_operator\">)</span> <span class=\"hl_operator\">⇒</span> <span class=\"hl_operator\">(</span>#i <span class=\"hl_operator\">=</span> #j<span class=\"hl_operator\">)</span>&quot;<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_comment\">// safety formula</span><br/>\n<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_comment\">/*<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;expanded formula:<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&quot;<span class=\"hl_operator\">∀ </span>#i #j<span class=\"hl_operator\">.</span><br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">(</span><span class=\"hl_operator\">(</span>Setup( ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">@</span> #i<span class=\"hl_operator\">)</span> <span class=\"hl_operator\">∧</span> <span class=\"hl_operator\">(</span>Setup( ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">@</span> #j<span class=\"hl_operator\">)</span><span class=\"hl_operator\">)</span> <span class=\"hl_operator\">⇒</span> <span class=\"hl_operator\">(</span>#i <span class=\"hl_operator\">=</span> #j<span class=\"hl_operator\">)</span>&quot;<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;*/</span></p><br/>\n","title":"Multiset rewriting rules and restrictions"}